<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>綠雷德感動玩linktree</title>

<style>
* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background: #A1D5F8;
    color: #fff;
}



/* 容器 */
.container {
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 20px;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    z-index: 1;
    min-height: 100vh;
}

.container::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('images/KV.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    opacity: 0.6;
    border-radius: 20px;
    z-index: -1;
}

.container::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 20px;
    z-index: -1;
}

/* 頭像 */
.profile {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
	position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
}

.profile img {
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}

/* 標題 */
.profile h1 {
    margin: 12px 0 10px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-family: actor;
    font-style: normal;
	
}

/* 新增活動資訊 */
.event-info {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

/* 卡片 */
.card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
}


/* 內容層（確保在最上面） */
.card > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}


/* 按鈕 */
.link-btn {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center; /* 文字置中 */
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin: 12px 0;
    border-radius: 50px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* 流光 */
.link-btn::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.4), transparent);
    transition: 0.6s;
}

.link-btn:hover::before {
    left: 100%;
}

.link-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}

/* icon */
.link-btn img {
    position: absolute;
    left: 15px; /* 固定左側 */
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
}


/* ripple */
.link-btn span.ripple {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: scale(0);
    animation: ripple 0.6s linear;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
}

@keyframes ripple {
    to {
        transform: scale(4);
        opacity: 0;
    }
}
body,td,th {
    font-family: amaranth;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
}
</style>
<!--The following script tag downloads a font from the Adobe Edge Web Fonts server for use within the web page. We recommend that you do not modify it.-->
<script>var __adobewebfontsappname__="dreamweaver"</script>
<script src="http://use.edgefonts.net/concert-one:n4:default;acme:n4:default;actor:n4:default;amaranth:n4:default.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="profile">
        <img src="images/LOGO@300x-8.png">
        <h1>綠雷德感動玩</h1>

        <div class="event-info">
            🦈 Baby Shark 守護海洋大冒險🦈 <br>
            日期：2026 年 4 月 17 日 – 2026 年 6 月 21 日 <br>
            地點：國立臺灣科學教育館7樓西側特展廳<br>
            （臺北市士林區士商路 189 號）
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
		

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://tr.ee/vO300N0t3T" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/FB logo.jpg">
            <div class="link-text">Facebook綠雷德感動玩</div>
        </a>

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://kidsfun.tw/klk" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/01@300x-8.png">
        <div class="link-text">Klook</div>
        </a>

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://kidsfun.tw/acp" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/02@300x-8.png">
            <div class="link-text">ACCUPASS</div>
        </a>

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://kidsfun.tw/kkd" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/03@300x-8.png">
            <div class="link-text">KKday</div>
        </a>

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://kidsfun.tw/ibon" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/04@300x-8.png">
            <div class="link-text">ibon</div>
        </a>

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://kidsfun.tw/udn" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/05@300x-8.png">
            <div class="link-text">udn</div>
        </a>

        <a class="link-btn" href="https://kidsfun.tw/fami" target="_blank">
            <img src="images/06@300x-8.png">
            <div class="link-text">全網Fami ticket</div>
        </a>

    </div>

</div>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.link-btn').forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        const circle = document.createElement('span');
        circle.classList.add('ripple');

        const rect = this.getBoundingClientRect();
        circle.style.left = e.clientX - rect.left + 'px';
        circle.style.top = e.clientY - rect.top + 'px';

        this.appendChild(circle);
        setTimeout(() => circle.remove(), 600);
    });
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
